msgid "# RFork Guide"
msgstr "# RFork 指南"

msgid ""
"This guide explains how to use **RFork** as a model-loader plugin in **vLLM "
"Ascend**."
msgstr "本指南说明如何在 **vLLM Ascend** 中将 **RFork** 用作模型加载器插件。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使用方法"

msgid ""
"To enable RFork, pass `--load-format rfork` and provide RFork settings "
"through `--model-loader-extra-config` as a JSON string."
msgstr ""
"要启用 RFork，请传递 `--load-format rfork` 并通过 `--model-loader-extra-config` 以 JSON"
" 字符串形式提供 RFork 设置。"

msgid "### RFork Prerequisites"
msgstr "### RFork 前提条件"

msgid ""
"- Install the runtime dependency `YuanRong TransferEngine` on every RFork instance.\n"
"- Run a planner service that implements the RFork seed protocol. A simple mock planner script is provided at [`rfork_planner.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/examples/rfork/rfork_planner.py)."
msgstr ""
"- 在每个 RFork 实例上安装运行时依赖 `YuanRong TransferEngine`。\n"
"- 运行一个实现 RFork seed 协议的规划器服务。一个简单的模拟规划器脚本位于 [`rfork_planner.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/examples/rfork/rfork_planner.py)。"

msgid "### Configuration Fields"
msgstr "### 配置字段"

msgid ""
"| Field Name | Type | Description | Allowed Values / Notes |\n"
"|------------|------|-------------|------------------------|\n"
"| **model_url** | String | Logical model identifier used to build the RFork seed key. | Required for RFork transfer. Instances that should share seeds must use the same value. |\n"
"| **model_deploy_strategy_name** | String | Deployment strategy identifier used together with `model_url` to build the seed key. | Required for RFork transfer. Instances that should share seeds must use the same value. |\n"
"| **rfork_scheduler_url** | String | Base URL of the planner service used for seed allocation, release, and heartbeat. | Required for planner-based matching. Example: `http://127.0.0.1:1223`. |\n"
"| **rfork_seed_timeout_sec** | Number | Timeout for waiting until the local seed HTTP service becomes healthy after startup. | Optional. Default: `5.0`. Must be greater than `0`. Invalid values fall back to the default. |\n"
"| **rfork_seed_key_separator** | String | Separator used when building the RFork seed key string. | Optional. Default: `$`. Keep the same value across compatible instances. |"
msgstr ""
"| 字段名 | 类型 | 描述 | 允许值/说明 |\n"
"|------------|------|-------------|------------------------|\n"
"| **model_url** | 字符串 | 用于构建 RFork seed 键的逻辑模型标识符。 | RFork 传输必需。应共享 seed 的实例必须使用相同的值。 |\n"
"| **model_deploy_strategy_name** | 字符串 | 与 `model_url` 一起用于构建 seed 键的部署策略标识符。 | RFork 传输必需。应共享 seed 的实例必须使用相同的值。 |\n"
"| **rfork_scheduler_url** | 字符串 | 用于 seed 分配、释放和心跳的规划器服务的基础 URL。 | 基于规划器的匹配必需。示例：`http://127.0.0.1:1223`。 |\n"
"| **rfork_seed_timeout_sec** | 数字 | 等待本地 seed HTTP 服务在启动后变为健康状态的超时时间。 | 可选。默认值：`5.0`。必须大于 `0`。无效值将回退到默认值。 |\n"
"| **rfork_seed_key_separator** | 字符串 | 构建 RFork seed 键字符串时使用的分隔符。 | 可选。默认值：`$`。在兼容的实例间保持相同的值。 |"

msgid "### How RFork Matches Seeds"
msgstr "### RFork 如何匹配 Seeds"

msgid ""
"RFork does not match instances by `model_url` alone. The local seed key is "
"composed from:"
msgstr "RFork 不单独通过 `model_url` 匹配实例。本地 seed 键由以下部分组成："

msgid ""
"- `model_url`\n"
"- `model_deploy_strategy_name`\n"
"- disaggregation mode derived from `kv_transfer_config.kv_role` or `kv_both`\n"
"- `node_rank`\n"
"- `pp_rank` when pipeline parallel size is greater than 1\n"
"- `tp_rank`\n"
"- `ep_rank` when expert parallelism is enabled for an MoE model\n"
"- optional `draft` suffix when the worker runs as a draft model"
msgstr ""
"- `model_url`\n"
"- `model_deploy_strategy_name`\n"
"- 从 `kv_transfer_config.kv_role` 或 `kv_both` 派生的分离模式\n"
"- `node_rank`\n"
"- 当流水线并行大小大于 1 时的 `pp_rank`\n"
"- `tp_rank`\n"
"- 当 MoE 模型启用专家并行时的 `ep_rank`\n"
"- 当工作器作为草稿模型运行时的可选 `draft` 后缀"

msgid ""
"This means two instances must agree on both model identity and deployment topology before the planner will treat them as interchangeable seeds.\n"
"For deployments without pipeline or expert parallelism, the existing seed-key format is unchanged."
msgstr ""
"这意味着两个实例必须在模型标识和部署拓扑上达成一致，规划器才会将它们视为可互换的 seed。\n"
"对于没有流水线或专家并行的部署，现有的 seed 键格式保持不变。"

msgid "### Quantized Models"
msgstr "### 量化模型"

msgid ""
"For quantized models, RFork transfers tensors after Ascend weight post-"
"processing instead of raw checkpoint parameters. The receiver first builds "
"the same post-load tensor layout as the seed, then RFork copies the live NPU"
" tensors used by inference."
msgstr ""
"对于量化模型，RFork 在 Ascend 权重后处理之后传输张量，而不是原始检查点参数。接收方首先构建与 seed 相同的加载后张量布局，然后 "
"RFork 复制推理使用的活跃 NPU 张量。"

msgid ""
"This path handles Ascend quantization changes such as weight transposition, "
"NZ format conversion, packed weights, derived scale tensors, and MLA/SFA "
"runtime tensors such as `W_UV` and `W_UK_T`. Empty tensors that were "
"released during post-processing are not included in the transfer manifest."
msgstr ""
"此路径处理 Ascend 量化更改，例如权重转置、NZ 格式转换、压缩权重、派生缩放张量以及 MLA/SFA 运行时张量（如 `W_UV` 和 "
"`W_UK_T`）。后处理期间释放的空张量不包含在传输清单中。"

msgid "When validating RFork for a quantized model:"
msgstr "验证量化模型的 RFork 时："

msgid ""
"- Apply the same vLLM Ascend code to both the seed instance and the receiver instance.\n"
"- Restart the planner and all vLLM instances after changing RFork code, because existing seeds keep their old transfer metadata.\n"
"- Use a new `model_deploy_strategy_name` after changing model arguments or RFork code, so the planner does not match a receiver with an incompatible old seed.\n"
"- A successful RFork transfer logs `transfer weights starts` and `transfer weights time`. The fallback path logs `RFork transfer failed`."
msgstr ""
"- 对 seed 实例和接收方实例应用相同的 vLLM Ascend 代码。\n"
"- 更改 RFork 代码后重新启动规划器和所有 vLLM 实例，因为现有的 seed 会保留其旧的传输元数据。\n"
"- 更改模型参数或 RFork 代码后使用新的 `model_deploy_strategy_name`，这样规划器就不会将接收方与不兼容的旧 seed 匹配。\n"
"- 成功的 RFork 传输会记录 `transfer weights starts` 和 `transfer weights time`。回退路径会记录 `RFork transfer failed`。"

